graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[React 18 SPA<br/>PatternFly UI]
        Backend[Node.js/Fastify Backend<br/>Port: 8080/TCP HTTP]
        Proxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Port: 8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OAuth2 Authentication]
        StaticServer[Static File Server<br/>Fastify Static]
        WebSocket[WebSocket Server<br/>Fastify WebSocket]

        Frontend -->|serves from| StaticServer
        Frontend -->|real-time updates| WebSocket
        Proxy -->|forwards auth requests| Backend
        Backend -->|serves| StaticServer
        Backend -->|manages| WebSocket
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources Watched"
        OdhApp[OdhApplication CR<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument CR<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart CR<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        DSC[DataScienceCluster CR]
        DSCI[DSCInitialization CR]
        InferenceService[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io]
        ModelRegistry[ModelRegistry CR<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io]
        Notebook[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org]
        FeatureStore[FeatureStore CR<br/>feast.dev]
        LlamaStack[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
        NotebookController[notebook-controller]
        KServeController[kserve-controller]
        ModelRegOp[model-registry-operator]
    end

    subgraph "Ingress"
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt]
        Gateway[Gateway HTTPRoute<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Passthrough]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS/443| Route
    User -->|HTTPS/443| Gateway
    Route -->|HTTPS/8443| Proxy
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/8443| Proxy

    Backend -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Proxy -->|OAuth2 flow| OAuth
    Backend -->|metrics queries| Thanos

    Backend -->|watches| OdhApp
    Backend -->|watches| OdhConfig
    Backend -->|watches| OdhDoc
    Backend -->|watches| QuickStart
    Backend -->|watches| DSC
    Backend -->|watches| DSCI
    Backend -->|watches| InferenceService
    Backend -->|watches| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|creates/manages| Notebook
    Backend -->|watches| FeatureStore
    Backend -->|watches| LlamaStack

    Backend -->|integrates| NotebookController
    Backend -->|integrates| KServeController
    Backend -->|integrates| ModelRegOp

    style Frontend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Backend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Proxy fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
